item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

These are the male and female wield model ids.
class8.anInt165 = 7355;
class8.anInt200 = 7244;
This is the ground model id (the model that shows on the ground when you drop it, and the one in your inventory)
class8.anInt174 = 7354;//item look
I assume these are going to be in a folder in your cache named models or raw or something.
Use RSMV (RS Model Viewer) to look at the models, check to see if they are teletab models or godsword models
